value.string:
SELECT HSA.AgencyID,

       HSA.AgencyNumber,

       HSC.FirstName,

       HSC.LastName,

       HSC.Email

FROM dbo.HS_AGENCY HSA

    JOIN dbo.HS_CONTACT HSC

        ON HSC.FKID = HSA.AgencyID

WHERE HSC.ParentEntity = 2

      AND HSA.Active = 1

      AND HSC.Active = 1

      AND HSC.Email <> '';
